Pfleiderer CEO Offered to Step Down, Euro am Sonntag Reports

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-03-05T13:51:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-05/pfleiderer-ceo-offered-to-step-down-euro-am-sonntag-reports.html
  Pfleiderer AG (PFD4)  Chief Executive
Officer Hans Overdiek offered to resign,  Euro am Sonntag 
reported, citing unidentified people familiar with the matter.  The offer was not taken up, the newspaper said. The only
option to save the company is a debt write-off by creditors,
Euro am Sonntag said, citing unidentified people in the banking
industry.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Andreas Cremer in Berlin at 
 acremer@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:  Kenneth Wong  at   kwong11@bloomberg.net . 